    "form_header_text": "FY 2027 Appropriations Request Form",
    "form_instructions_text": "One of Congress's most fundamental constitutional duties is the appropriations process -- the annual allocation of funds for federal discretionary programs. As a senior member of the House Appropriations Committee, I intend to fight for initiatives that are the most important for Georgia's Second Congressional District. This form is for organizations to make requests for funding levels of authorized federal programs and/or submit requested bill language or report language. Directions: Please fill in each field, including writing \"NA\" in fields that do not apply for your request. Upon completion, save and submit this form via email to GA02.appropriations@mail.house.gov. Please only send one attachment per email. The subject line should include the appropriations subcommittee name and the name of the account under which you are making your request.",
